snippet.title: Neon Abyss Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Neon Abyss is coming to Nintendo Switch, Xbox One, PlayStation 4 and PC on July 14th 2020!

Neon Abyss is a frantic run'n'gun roguelike where you'll face tough bosses in the form of new gods in the abyss! Death, is not the end as you'll unlock more items, characters, mini games and even bosses in your runs!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/788100/Neon_Abyss/

Official Website: https://www.veewo.com/neonabyss
Follow Veewo Games on  https://twitter.com/veewogames 
Follow Team17 on Twitter: https://twitter.com/Team17Ltd
Like Team17 on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Team17/

#NeonAbyss #Roguelite #NintendoSwitch #XboxOne #PS4

About Team17 Digital Ltd
Founded in 1990, Team17 Digital Limited is a leading international games label that hosts the Worms franchise, The Survivalists, The Escapists, Epic Chef, Overcooked, Hell Let Loose, My Time At Portia, Yooka-Laylee and many more from developers around the world. Visit www.team17.com for more info.
